<div class="cms-copy-rsp" >
    
        <p style="text-align: center;">For example, we collect notes from our conversations with you, details of any complaints or comments you make, details of purchases you made, items viewed or added to your basket, gift list and wish list choices, voucher redemptions, brands you show interest in, web pages you visit and how and when you contact us.<br>
</p>

    
