<p>We then use this to offer you promotions, products and services that are most likely to interest you. In the case of loyalty scheme members, weâll also offer you relevant rewards.</p>
<p>The data privacy law allows this as part of our legitimate interest in understanding our customers and providing the highest levels of service.</p>
<p>Of course, if you wish to change how we use your data, youâll find details in the âWhat are my rights?â section below.</p>
