    <section class="  cms-accordion-item2 cms-accordion-item2--no-padding">
  <h2 class="cms-accordion-item2__title"><span>8. How we protect your personal data</span></h2>

  <div class="cms-accordion-item2__description">
  <div class="cms-grid-container">
    <div class="col"
  aria-hidden="false"
>

<div class="cms-divider-rsp cms-divider-whitespace-medium"></div>
</div>


<div class="col col-lg-12 offset-lg-0"
  aria-hidden="false"
>

<div class="cms-copy-rsp" >
    
        <p>We know how much data security matters to all our customers. With this in mind we will treat your data with the utmost care and take all appropriate steps to protect it.</p>
<p>We secure access to all transactional areas of our websites and apps using âhttpsâ technology.</p>
<p>Access to your personal data is password-protected,&nbsp;and sensitive data such as payment card information) is secured and tokenised to ensure it is protected. </p>
<p>We regularly monitor our system for possible vulnerabilities and attacks, and we carry out penetration testing to identify ways to further strengthen security.<br>
</p>

    
</div>
</div>



  </div>
</div>

</section>

  
