  <h2 class="cms-accordion-item2__title"><span>9. How long will we keep your personal data?</span></h2>

  <div class="cms-accordion-item2__description">
  <div class="cms-grid-container">
    <div class="col"
  aria-hidden="false"
>

<div class="cms-divider-rsp cms-divider-whitespace-medium"></div>
</div>


<div class="col col-lg-12 offset-lg-0"
  aria-hidden="false"
>

<div class="cms-copy-rsp" >
    
        <p>Whenever we collect or process your personal data, weâll only keep it for as long as is necessary for the purpose for which it was collected. </p>
<p><br>
At the end of that retention period, your data will either be deleted completely or anonymised, for example by aggregation with other data so that it can be used in a non-identifiable way for statistical analysis and business planning.<br>
</p>

    
</div>
</div>


<div class="col"
  aria-hidden="false"
